entries.femaleVariant: Look, you can always land one like this.
Don't work with the new ones, though.
This one's got a motion sensor, only reacts when you move.
Hah, you know what ranks they got? Wolves 'n' Weasels.
Choom, come on. Don't give me that bullshit.
Mhm. Ours is a Wolf, obviously. Just look at it.
'Course, might just seem that way to us Weasels.
I mean, yeah I'd watch one or two just to pass the time, but he's sittin' there all day...
He gotta have that whole theater to himself?
Them old-school movies, pretty sure they didn't work like that.
I mean, shit, I'm at work here.
So's he. Just getting more eddies for it.
What if there's nothin' left on the Net?
Why don't you jack in and find out?
I'm serious, choom. What if they killed off all the AIs? And it's just NetWatch sittin' in there?
And what're they doin' there alone?
Prolly not much. Maybe just talkin' 'bout boogiemen and takin' corpo cash. And jerkin' off their rhino horns.
Heheheh. That would scare off a netrunner for sure.
New models got muscle memory sims. React to your intention, not your move.
Meanin' what? The new ones know what I'm gonna do before I do it?
An' this one I can just pound into the ground?
Yep. 'Zackly.
Jesus, I handled it. Chill the fuck out.
OK, fine. I'm headed to the ring now. Later.
Buhhh...
Oh shit, did you see that?
Hey choomba, you still breathin'?
Hey, c'mere! This scrap bucket actually works.
I'm comin'.
Oh, that robot-fuck lit you up, dude!
I think he cracked his ribs!
Somethin' here seems off...
